job.title: GAIL (India) Ltd Various Vacancy Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 220 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:220

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Manager, Senior Engineer  

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates has been published by the Gas Authority of India Limited for Manager vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Manager, from 07-07-2021, and till the last date05-08-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a manager in Gas Authority of India Limited, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 07-07-2021 at 11:00 Hrs
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 05-08-2021 by 18:00 Hrs

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

GAIL Manager Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

Detailed vacancies:

How to apply for GAIL (India) Ltd Various Vacancy Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Manager. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of GAIL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by GAIL
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
